    {
      "chinese": "民國六十年以前，女性結婚時一定要哭，哭泣有固定旋律，也有哭詞。女方從婚談成功、商定結婚日期起，從居家縫衣、刺繡，到田野除草，都要不斷練習哭泣，天天以哭詞向親人，尤其對男性友人訴苦，表達不贊同這樁婚姻，哀悼將和玩伴離別。",
      "ab": "ki mingkuku manemele ka caili papucucubungu, lu aikahudrange kai ababai tahawatubi, yakai ku lingau lutubi, laikai ku saiyaiya. twalai lu mapalrailraingi la madrekadrekasenga ku atapikaiya ka vai pathagili, adrava lu tangeangea itauwana cwaicaisi, pwacapacase si lu mumawma tulravai, aitubitubi kicakuwa, ki vaivai ki vaivai aikicakwakuwa tubi, ahatubi kiasa ki lahetesa lalyali lasyasilanga, ku kadruwa ka tapalrainganeini ikai lrauga, ku sataulraulraneini lu kalaelaelange.",
      "order": "2",
